{"tid":1336632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【重溫水性】請唔好忘記李小龍嘅water其實有兩個行動形態，唔係淨係「散」","createTime":"2019-07-21T04:55:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T07:31:16.000Z","uid":131691,"like":90,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"147564682e72c97dcf9bf4354a45bf684abb0bc7","tid":1336632,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T04:55:40.000Z","msg":"李小龍講嘅be water，其實有三點。<br />\n<br />\n1，if you put water into a bottle, it becomes the bottle; if you put it in a teapot, it becomes the teapot.<br />\n<br />\n簡單講，即係要識得應變。由六月開始嘅抗爭AI就係咁，遊行，衝擊，不合作，「道歉」，攻城，連儂，起底，登報，日日唔同，對唔同嘅audience，放唔同嘅文宣，多面夾攻政府。<br />\n<br />\n2，water can flow<br />\n<br />\n唔長期佔路，唔死守連儂，傷自己士氣又唔可以傷敵人嘅，無謂死守。<br />\n<br />\n3，or it can crash<br />\n<br />\n香港人仲未做到呢點：flow嚟flow去，有虛位，就要如洪水般淹沒敵人"},{"pid":"d8fcc09ef5ea3e14e01fd23b790939747feb0b54","tid":1336632,"uid":131691,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T04:58:01.000Z","msg":"希望群眾會進化到第三點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb4b099061745d4fa1028f3871c39bb27d778779","tid":1336632,"uid":28257,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T05:02:25.000Z","msg":"其實FLOW都未算做到最好<br />\n<br />\n總有人唔肯退 總有人退得太快"},{"pid":"1c9498a77e08ad3309527906c362006c1493dba7","tid":1336632,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T05:02:57.000Z","msg":"散 聚 <br />\n<br />\n上善若水，水善利萬物而不爭，處為人之所惡，故幾於道。<br />\n<br />\n居善地，心善淵，與善仁，言善信，正善治，事善能，動善時。夫唯不爭，故無尤。"},{"pid":"d35de27038eac4480c066f1bac404ac4dcb3fba3","tid":1336632,"uid":53498,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T05:04:28.000Z","msg":"沙田一役如果搬去今日,我覺得好大機會crash,人數加憤怒"},{"pid":"6210ab2f3719fbaa67a724e2c30220dc8e90c780","tid":1336632,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb4b099061745d4fa1028f3871c39bb27d778779","tid":1336632,"uid":28257,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T05:02:25.000Z","msg":"其